## 🔄 Type Inference 플로우

### 예제 코드

```freelang
fn add(x, y) {
  return x + y
}

let result = add(10, 20)
```

### 타입 추론 흐름

```
1️⃣ TypeChecker.check(program)

2️⃣ First Pass: registerFunctionType()
   add → {paramTypes: [UNKNOWN, UNKNOWN], returnType: UNKNOWN}

3️⃣ Second Pass: checkStmt("fn")
   • x, y를 env에 UNKNOWN으로 등록
   • return x + y 분석
     - x: UNKNOWN, y: UNKNOWN
     - getOperationResultType("+", UNKNOWN, UNKNOWN) → UNKNOWN
   • currentFunctionReturnTypes.push(UNKNOWN)
   • inferReturnType([UNKNOWN]) → UNKNOWN

4️⃣ functionTypes 갱신
   add → {paramTypes: [UNKNOWN, UNKNOWN], returnType: UNKNOWN}

5️⃣ Call 검증: add(10, 20)
   • 인자 개수 확인: 2 == 2 ✓
   • 인자 타입 검증:
     - argType[0] = num, paramType[0] = UNKNOWN → compatible ✓
     - argType[1] = num, paramType[1] = UNKNOWN → compatible ✓
   • 반환 타입: UNKNOWN

결과: ✓ 타입 체크 통과
```

